In~\Fig{radar} we show a radar plot that compares our two measures with current standards for four qubits~\cite{PhysRevA.65.052112} and we see that each state describes a unique path in this plot. 
Comparing entanglement measures in this way may help characterise entanglement within systems of qubits, spins, or two-level atoms.

